            <li><strong>Payment Holiday:</strong> Temporary payment pause (1-3 months) with added tenure</li>
            <li><strong>Partial Payment:</strong> Pay what you can afford to show commitment</li>
            <li><strong>Refinancing:</strong> New loan with better terms to settle existing loan</li>
          </ul>

