              <li><strong>Express Delivery Jobs:</strong> Take higher-margin urgent deliveries</li>
              <li><strong>Sub-Contracting:</strong> Rent out your lorry to other operators</li>
              <li><strong>Backload Optimization:</strong> Fill return trips with cargo (addresses 77% empty backload issue)</li>
              <li><strong>Temporary Downgrade:</strong> Switch to shorter routes or lighter cargo temporarily</li>
            </ul>
