              <ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-2">
                <li>Modify existing loan terms</li>
                <li>No new loan application</li>
                <li>Lower monthly payments</li>
                <li>Longer tenure (more interest)</li>
                <li>Same financier relationship</li>
              </ul>
